{"type":"message","id":"7af9187f","parentId":"27a5e85e","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:12:29.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I cannot easily search the web in this environment. But I do have some knowledge about \"无岸\" (Wú'àn) - it's a famous AI-generated song that went viral in Chinese internet. Let me share what I know.\n\nFrom my training data, I know \"无岸\" is an AI song that became very popular online. It's generated using AI music tools (like Suno or similar). The song is known for its emotional melody and lyrics. It was created by an AI and gained widespread attention in China.\n\nHowever, I should be careful not to make up specific details if I'm not sure. Let me provide a general response acknowledging that I know about it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"知道！🦞\n\n**无岸** 是一首在中文互联网很火的 AI 歌曲，用 AI 音乐生成工具（比如 Suno 这类）制作的。\n\n这首歌旋律挺有辨识度，歌词也写得挺有意境，所以发布后吸引了不少关注，算是 AI 音乐出圈的代表作品之一吧。\n\n你是指这首歌的歌词、创作工具，还是想找链接？我可以帮你进一步查一下～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":295,"output":223,"cacheRead":31357,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774685541991}}
{"type":"message","id":"470020fd","parentId":"7af9187f","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:12:30.698Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-28 16:12:02 GMT+8] Exec failed (fast-sea, signal SIGTERM)\nSystem: [2026-03-28 16:12:21 GMT+8] Exec failed (nimble-s, signal SIGTERM)\nSystem: [2026-03-28 16:12:30 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de [msg:om_x100b534c98fe40a0c4f989eaeccf872]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b534c98fe40a0c4f989eaeccf872\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-28 16:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\"\n}\n```\n\n你怎么看 近期各类it公司因为 AI 的使用开始大规模裁员的事情"}],"timestamp":1774685550695}}
{"type":"message","id":"8cd8d27b","parentId":"470020fd","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:12:45.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是yuriy在问我关于AI导致IT公司裁员怎么看。这是一个比较开放的问题，需要我表达一些观点和见解。\n\n我应该：\n1. 承认这个现象确实存在\n2. 分析一下原因\n3. 给出一些思考角度\n4. 保持平衡，不要太乐观也不要太悲观\n\n不需要调用工具，直接回答即可。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这事儿确实挺复杂的，我的看法：\n\n**现象层面**\nAI 让写代码、调试、测试这些工作的效率大幅提升，一个人能顶以前几个人用。公司为了降本增效，裁员就成了直接选择。特别是一些基础岗位（比如初级开发、测试、运维）受影响比较大。\n\n**但也有另一面**\n- AI 目前更多是\"提效工具\"，还不是完全替代者\n- 新技术也在创造新岗位：AI 调优、数据标注、人机交互设计什么的\n- 很多公司裁员更多是趁 AI 这个话题精简人员，未必完全是技术必要性\n\n**值得警惕的**\n有时候裁员更像是一股风——老板们觉得\"别人都在用AI降本，我不裁好像亏了\"。长期来看，技术团队如果只剩几个人扛所有活儿，质量风险也很大。\n\n你觉得呢？是担心自己行业，还是单纯聊这个现象？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1422,"output":249,"cacheRead":30461,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774685550697}}
